To CHECKOUT project from github:

set .ssh key as described here - http://help.github.com/linux-set-up-git/
then

mkdir tennis-trader
cd tennis-trader
git init
git remote add origin git@github.com:paul-g/tennis-trader.git
git pull -u origin master

To RUN:

  FOR 32 bit JVM on LINUX:
     Set Makefile.local LIN_VER = 32

  FOR 64 BIT JVM ON LINUX:
     Set Makefile.local LIN_VER = 64

  THEN
    cd tennis-trader
    make
    
  BUILD:
	  make build

  RUN:
	  make run
	
If everything is OK, you should see a window with a tree list pop up.

p.s. ANT SCRIPT IS COMING....


